{"tid":1256082,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"目標不是異世界，兩大聲優「優梶裕貴及竹達彩奈結婚」竟引發網民「投胎轉生潮」？","createTime":"2019-06-24T22:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T03:30:02.000Z","uid":75050,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5a2b4a7ef82cb94a54bf89fd4cc45bf5ff45a0","tid":1256082,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T22:49:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://game.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=19980804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D19980804&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443q%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9c6366ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://game.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=19980804</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>目標不是異世界，兩大聲優結婚竟引發網民「投胎轉生潮」？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n兩大人氣聲優梶裕貴及竹達彩奈昨日宣布結婚，網上除了有大量Fans為兩人獻上祝福，亦意外地出現了一個搞笑的「投胎轉生潮」，就是有網民打算以成為兩人的孩子為目標轉生！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.uwants.com/attachments/day_190624/20190624_9fbf5e439a074b07ef115MsytqMskIbZ.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.uwants.com%2Fattachments%2Fday_190624%2F20190624_9fbf5e439a074b07ef115MsytqMskIbZ.jpg%3F&h=bc123d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日婚訊公開後，有人在Twitter的搜尋欄中發現「竹達彩奈 死」的字眼，誰不知按進去後看到的竟是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>現在去死的話，可以轉生成竹達彩奈的孩子的可能性十分高。再見了各位</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.uwants.com/attachments/day_190624/20190624_25250fbfb22bb3cff17fMuTFhkLuDrrt.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.uwants.com%2Fattachments%2Fday_190624%2F20190624_25250fbfb22bb3cff17fMuTFhkLuDrrt.png%3F&h=315817a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>咦！？現在死去就有機會成為這對俊男美女的孩子嗎？那我去死囉</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.uwants.com/attachments/day_190624/20190624_4c8ddaff2889befea018TopxvYqtg5zh.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.uwants.com%2Fattachments%2Fday_190624%2F20190624_4c8ddaff2889befea018TopxvYqtg5zh.png%3F&h=1f49e70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>現在的話還有機會成為竹達彩奈的孩子！你們快點去死啊！</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.uwants.com/attachments/day_190624/20190624_0d5e3d030985ce9d9374YzK4lcnVu6UW.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.uwants.com%2Fattachments%2Fday_190624%2F20190624_0d5e3d030985ce9d9374YzK4lcnVu6UW.png%3F&h=d95862ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本以為會是因婚訊而感到不滿的人，沒想到竟然是一群笑說要投胎轉生的網民！當中還有<strong><ins>「希望能被竹達彩奈餵哺」、「希望能被梶裕貴抱着」</ins></strong>等更仔細的願望&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>雖說大家都知道這只是說笑而已，不過還是希望不會有人真的因此而自殺啊</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.uwants.com/attachments/day_190624/20190624_92e8f5f8d10e3916d16bOE1t3ekRfwU1.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.uwants.com%2Fattachments%2Fday_190624%2F20190624_92e8f5f8d10e3916d16bOE1t3ekRfwU1.png%3F&h=4a599b96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98d25b9f5d58061f9621b8d6e999e2df6b4d558d","tid":1256082,"uid":240608,"like":22,"dislike":11,"score":11,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T23:23:56.000Z","msg":"個女都唔靚"},{"pid":"e4e1b7f50acb7676876faadc5a058628e23897a0","tid":1256082,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98d25b9f5d58061f9621b8d6e999e2df6b4d558d","tid":1256082,"uid":240608,"like":22,"dislike":11,"score":11,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T23:23:56.000Z","msg":"個女都唔靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d993f849a7094490adeadf3603a9423ceef4b6d","tid":1256082,"uid":21456,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"98d25b9f5d58061f9621b8d6e999e2df6b4d558d","tid":1256082,"uid":240608,"like":22,"dislike":11,"score":11,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T23:23:56.000Z","msg":"個女都唔靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:33:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3858137ae4dbc12ea9b60abb708526b86167f7de","tid":1256082,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98d25b9